reviews.review_text:
ooh yea! thank you for attenuating that horrible noise present in slipknot.   apparently it was the death cry of a battery in one of garcia's pedals.

recording is punchy and clear - and garcia is playing very fluidly, especially in the jstraw > sugaree opener.

thanks andrewf!
